snippet: Darrun Hilliard and Dylan Ennis each scored 15 points to lead No. 10 Villanova to an 84-70 win over La Salle on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: No. 10 Villanova Rolls Past La Salle 84-70
headline.main: No. 10 Villanova Rolls Past La Salle 84-70

lead_paragraph: Darrun Hilliard and Dylan Ennis each scored 15 points to lead No. 10 Villanova to an 84-70 win over La Salle on Wednesday night.
